text: Tim McCormack is a politician from Euclid, Ohio.Tim McCormack's Bio - The Lakewood Observer Retrieved 2018-05-20. He has served in a wide array of positions ranging from Commissioner, Auditor, as well as Euclid City Councilman, State Representative, and State Senator. He is currently a Judge of the Ohio Court of Appeals in the Eighth Appellate District.http://www.wkyc.com/news/news_article.aspx?storyid=125178 ==External links== *Court of Appeals: Tim McCormack ==References== Category:1940s births Category:Living people Category:Ohio state senators Category:People from Euclid, Ohio
